---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Hiro マーカー | discARd</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      background: #fff;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      gap: 24px;
      padding: 24px;
      font-family: sans-serif;
    }
    img {
      width: min(80vw, 80vh);
      height: min(80vw, 80vh);
      image-rendering: pixelated;
    }
    p { color: #555; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; }
    a { color: #5865F2; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <img src={`${base}/hiro.png`} alt="Hiro AR Marker" />
  <p>このマーカーを別の画面に表示して<br>AR カメラで読み取ってください</p>
  <a href={`${base}/`}>← トップへ戻る</a>
</body>
</html>
